thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Vanessa

author: Vanessa
title: Vanessa
text: I dont hate these guys but theres better out there. They were way too costly and rude to my children for playing in the boxes that I was paying big bucks for. It made it a horrible experience and made me bitter about handing them the extra surprise costs at the end. I kept my mouth closed but i'll definitely avoid them in future
